# Day 1- A band name generator
print("Can't think of a band name? Here's something that can help- \n")
#2. Ask the user for the city that they grew up in.
a = input("What is the name of the city you grew up in? \n")
#3. Ask the user for the name of a pet.
b = input("What pet would you like to have?\n")
#4. Combine the name of their city and pet and show them their band name.
print("Your band's name could be- "+ a + " " + b + "\n")
